thread.title: José Holder
thread.title_full: Victory Tax Solutions reviewed by José Holder

author: José Holder
title: José Holder
text:
Starla and Eric went above and beyond to put me in a position to be able to continue to provide for my two daughters as a single parent.I lost my wife to breast cancer two years ago and it's been rough and the bills have been piling up. I can't express enough about the burden that has been lifted off of me and my family. I can go to sleep at night now knowing that i no longer have to worry about the letters and the phone calls. THANK YOU VICTORY FROM THE BOTTOM OF MY HEART.
JOSÉ HOLDER
